      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
______*    if        rf-osr-snx-3qt       not  = 0
______*              move  "S"            to   w-exe-flg-spn          .
       exe-cph-lv3-qtv-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Apertura cella in funzione della quantita'      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
